      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Priced at $17,900, this older vehicle is in fair overall condition and represented honestly. It runs and drives and can serve well as dependable basic transportation, but it does show clear age and wear inside and out. Expect cosmetic blemishes, a used interior, and the kind of minor imperfections that come with an older vehicle, though nothing is being overstated or hidden. A practical choice for someone looking for usable transportation at a reasonable price without expecting a like-new car.",
