      "description": "Affordable and dependable transportation at a budget-friendly price. This vehicle is best suited for buyers seeking practical value, with the kind of honest wear you would expect at this price point. A sensible choice for commuting, a first car, or a project opportunity\u2014priced to sell and ready for its next owner.",
