      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels without the drama? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it starts, drives, and offers a solid budget-friendly option for someone who needs dependable transportation, a handy runabout, or a project to tidy up over time. It\u2019s being priced fairly for what it is, and if you\u2019re after honest value rather than showroom sparkle, this one could be a great fit. Happy to chat and answer questions openly.",
